xrootd-doc in epel-7

This page displays detail informations of the xrootd-doc package. You might want go back to the main page of xrootd-doc.

Changelog

Date Author Change
2020-11-18 Mattias Ellert - 1:5.0.3-2 - Correct plugin version checking to prevent false negatives - Fix wrong section number in xrootdfs.1 manpage - Use system tinyxml library (unbundle)
2020-11-12 Mattias Ellert - 1:5.0.3-1 - Update to version 5.0.3 - Drop patches (accepted upstream or previously backported)
2020-11-02 Mattias Ellert - 1:5.0.2-2 - Fix for XrdPosix failing to compile with glibc 2.33 (2.32.9000)
2020-09-18 Mattias Ellert - 1:5.0.2-1 - Update to version 5.0.2 - Drop patches (accepted upstream or previously backported) - Obsolete xrdhttpvoms in xrootd-voms package
2020-08-27 Mattias Ellert - 1:5.0.1-1 - Update to version 5.0.1 - Remove conditionals for building on EPEL 6 - Drop patches (accepted upstream or previously backported) - Fix 32 bit compilation (format error) - Fix compilation on ARM, PPC and S390X (char is unsigned)
2020-08-26 Mattias Ellert - 1:4.12.3-5 - Use new CMake macros where available - Backport minor fixes from upstream git - Correct flag reset code for ssq monitor option - Fix typo in xrootd-config help - Prevent deadlock in Python bindings - Fix plugin path in xrootd-http.cfg for 32 bit architectures
2020-07-29 Fedora Release Engineering - 1:4.12.3-4 - Rebuilt for https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_33_Mass_Rebuild
2020-07-24 Mattias Ellert - 1:4.12.3-3 - Fix one definition rule (ODR) violation for LTO - Disable LTO for 32 bit architectures due to the POSIX preload code
2020-07-16 Mattias Ellert - 1:4.12.3-2 - Fix a typo in the rpm scriptlets (missing underscore)
2020-07-13 Mattias Ellert - 1:4.12.3-1 - Update to version 4.12.3 (no code changes w.r.t. 4.12.2) - Backport XrdVoms fixes from upstream git
